\over r^4}(\fa +\fb +\fc)\right ]+ \cr
&-e^{-2f_2}\biggl (f_{0,2}\fx_{,2}+ {\fa_{,2}\over r}\biggr )-\Delta, \cr}
\eqn\disettec
$$
$$
\eqalign{
